                        "displayName": "Helgi Hrafn Halld\u00f3rsson",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It would be great  to know if this will be fixed soon ? and if so when ? :D\n\nI saw this did not come in the 1.5.2 release :(",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=harabanar",
                        "name": "harabanar",
                        "displayName": "Helgi Hrafn Halld\u00f3rsson",
